# Plot MNIST t-SNE

sns.set_style("ticks")

sns.lmplot(x='_DIM_1_',
           y='_DIM_2_',
           data=tsne_MNIST_out,
           fit_reg=False,
           legend=True,
           size=9,
           hue='Label',
           scatter_kws={"s":200, "alpha":0.3})

plt.xlabel('Dimension 1', weight='bold').set_fontsize('10')
plt.ylabel('Dimension 2', weight='bold').set_fontsize('10')
